<topic id='business_definition_ambulance_control_room.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>NHS Business Definition: Ambulance Control Room - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>

  <p>
An 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_ambulance_control_room">Ambulance Control Room</xref>
 is a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_service">SERVICE</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
An 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_ambulance_control_room">Ambulance Control Room</xref>
 is provided by an 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_ambulance_service">Ambulance Service</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
An 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_ambulance_control_room">Ambulance Control Room</xref>
, also known as an 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_ambulance_control_room">Emergency Operations Centre (EOC)</xref>
, is provided by an 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_ambulance_service">Ambulance Service</xref>
 and is where 999 calls and calls from 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_professional">CARE PROFESSIONALS</xref>
 are received and triaged.  </p>
  <p>
A call can be a direct 999 call or a call transferred from another 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATION</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
      <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_ambulance_vehicle">AMBULANCE VEHICLES</xref>
 are dispatched from the 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_ambulance_control_room">Ambulance Control Room</xref>
 to respond to 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENTS</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
For further information on the 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_ambulance_control_room">Ambulance Control Room</xref>
 and its functions, see the 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_association_of_ambulance_chief_executives">Association of Ambulance Chief Executives</xref>
 website at: 
    <xref href="https://aace.org.uk" scope="external" format="html">AACE</xref>
.  </p>

